Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:27.30,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Shot down by Kushieda...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:28.55,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I close my eyes—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.55,0:23:29.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.93,0:23:30.97,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey-yo, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.97,0:23:32.68,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear her usual cheerful voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.68,0:23:34.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And, whoosh!
